snippet.title: ADOM -Ancient Domains of Mystery - Pyramid
snippet.description:
The pyramid is only accessible when your between level 13 and 17.  It has has 2 pretty good guaranteed artifacts - 
ANKH  
ANCIENT MUMMY WRAPPINGS 
plus a climbing set near the entrance , worth the trip
